column3: title
We have taken the enemy Sector! *Jubilous Laughter* (Any Sector)
We have taken Sector 1 from those dogs!
Comrades, great news, Sector 1 is ours!
Comrades, Sector 1 has been lost!
Cyka, Sector 1 has been taken!
Sector 2 has been captured from the enemy control!
Sector 2 has been taken, that was easy!
Sector 2 has been captured!
Sector 2 has been taken!
Sector 3 is taken, great work!
Sector 3 has been captured by our forces!
Sector 3 has been captured by the enemy!
Sector 3 is gone!
Sector 1 has been taken, now push on to the 2nd one Comrades!
BLYAT, Sector 1 is lost! Retreat to Sector 2 Comrades!
Sector 2 is now ours Comrades, lets push on to Sector 3 and end this fight!
Sector 2 is gone, they took it! Fallback to Sector 3 before it's too late Comrades!
Sector 3 is ours, Thank God, we can finally head home and drink Stoli!
Sector 3 is lost! Retreat!
Comrades, we blew up the objective, great job!
We are getting medals for blowing up that one!
*laughter*, another objective destroyed!
Boom! Great work Comrades!
CYKA, they blew up another objective!
They just destroyed our objective!
They blew it up, they blew up our objective!
Cyka, all hope is lost, fallback!
Pullback, we will get them next time!
BLYAT, the enemy have held their ground, fallback!
*cough* *cough*, everyone retreat.... (defeated sounding)
Fallback! I say again, fallback Comrades!
Retreat! Everyone retreat to the fallback line!
Everyone reading this, retreat to rally point Moscow!
Is anyone left? If you are reading this state your callsign and status!
We did it Comrades! We completed all objectives!
Oorah! We did it!
We pushed them so hard they just gave up! *laughing*
FOR THE MOTHERLAND! OORAH!
That was tougher than I thought it would be!
Mother Russia is proud of us Comrades!
THey stood no chance against Mother Russia!
Look at them run with their tail in between their legs! OORAHHHHHH!
We held our ground, good work Comrades!
Im thirsty for Stoli after that!
Wooh! I worked up a sweat for nothing!
Mother Russia now, Mother Russia FOREVER!
Enemy have paused our hack on the Terminal! (ANY TERMINAL)
The Terminal hack has been paused! (ANY TERMINAL)
We have hacked Terminal 1! Now push to the second one, OOOORAHHHHHH!
We just lost Terminal 1 Comrades! Retreat to the next Terminal!
Terminal 2 is hacked! Push to the final one! Come on Comrades!
We just lost the Second Terminal! Fallback!
Terminal 3 is done and hacked! We did it, FOR MOTHER RUSSIA! OOOOOORAAAAHHHHHH
Comrades, Terminal 3 has been hacked! The enemy have destroyed all of them!
Terminal 1 is done!
We just lost Terminal 1 Comrades!
We are hacking the first Terminal!
Enemy forces have begun a hack on Terminal 1!
Terminal 2 is done!
Blyat, Terminal 2 is lost!
We are hacking Terminal 2!
Terminal 2 is under attack!
Terminal 3 is done!
Comrades, Terminal 3 has been hacked!
Terminal 3 is under our control and being hacked!
THe enemy are hacking Terminal 3!
